title: Tina Organic Store and Restaurant
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Buffet, Salad bar, Take-out, Asian, Bakery, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic restaurant and store in Yingge District. Offers a small 3-choices menu plus a massive salad bar which is included in your meal purchase. Nice, calm atmosphere. Prices is slightly more than moderate, at around NT450-500 for a full meal with drink, dessert, salad/soup buffet. Or option for just the salad/soup bar.
